<br>HINDUSTANI MUSIC is the classical music of Northern regions of the indian subcontinent.It may also be called North Indian classical music or,in Hindustani,Shastriya Sangeet.The term Shastriya Sangeet literally means classical music,and can  also mean Indian classical music in general.</br>
