<div id="About">
    <h2>Course Information</h2>
</div>
<br>MUSIC is integral part of indian culture. To preserve and propagate indian music which include both Karnatic and Hindustani music,so we have came up with the idea of music courses which is one of the finest music training classes,which is located in,BurhanPuram,Khamam-urban,kahamam Distict, 507001.It is spread over very large area with numerous Class rooms. This music courses offers both South indian and North indian styles of music.</br>
<br>
<br>Student Age     : Min 10+(No upper age limit)</br>
